---
title: Sensory Composer — Live Performance Lifecycle
---
flowchart TD
    A([User Opens Audio Studio]) --> B[Browser requests\nmicrophone permission]
    B -->|Granted| C[Web Audio API\ncreates AnalyserNode]
    B -->|Denied| ERR([Show permission\nerror UI])
    C --> D[p5.js sketch reads\nFFT frequency data\nevery animation frame]
    D --> E[Canvas renders\nreal-time waveform\nand spectrum bars]
    E --> F{User clicks\nCapture?}
    F -->|No| D
    F -->|Yes| G[Audio snapshot\nbase64 encoded]
    G --> H[Poetry editor\ncontent collected]
    H --> I[Visual canvas\nexported as PNG]
    I --> J[Score package assembled:\naudio + visuals + poem]
    J --> K[Save to IndexedDB\n locally]
    K --> L[PouchDB syncs\npackage to CouchDB]
    L --> M[Laravel API\nreceives sync event]
    M --> N[FastAPI analyses\naudio features]
    N --> O[Results stored\nin PostgreSQL]
    O --> P([Score visible in\nAdmin Dashboard])
